quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  55,17,"Jey…óo fu…óir…óe naange ngen e lewru ndun e mutir…óe majje …óe, dabbunde e cee…óu."
  55,18,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,19,"Allah tuppindirii maaje …óen …ói…ói, ngo lam…óam e dee∆¥ungo, fottiray…óe no gite yiirata."
  55,20,"Heedo hino hakkunde kala majje, fii wata maayo goo jillondir e ngoya, hara maayo heddoday e ko heerori."
  55,21,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,22,"Hino yalta e …óen e …óen maaje kala : ka≈ã≈ãe "Lu'lu'u" e "Marjaan", njane e togoose."
  55,23,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,24,"Ko Kanko Senii…óo Toowu…óo On tun, woni ko yiilata laa…óe dogooje …óen ka maaje, wa'itay…óe wa pelle."
  55,25,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,26,"Kala tagoore ko woni e hoore leydi ndin, ko re'ay…óum feere mun alaa."
  55,27,"Heddoo Jaati Joomi maa Kin, an Nulaa…óo, Jom mawngu e mo∆¥∆¥ere, e …ìural e dow hoore jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ko Kanko tun woni fii lannataa poomaa."
  55,28,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,29,"Kala Malaa'ika ko woni ka kammuuli, e jinna e yim…ìe ko woni ka leydi fow no toroo Mo haaju mun. √ëalnde woo, Kanko Himo e fii fiyakuuji jiyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, immorde e wuurnitugol, e warugol, e arsikugol ekn."
  55,30,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,31,"Aray nde Men faandii hasbude on, onon yim…ìe e jinna, Men yo…ìa kala mon ko hanndi kon, immorde e baraaje maa lepte."
  55,32,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,33,"Si Allah moo…ìoyii jinna e yim…ìe √ëalnde Darngal, O daalana …ìe : ko onon yo dental jinna e yim…ìe ! Si on hattanii he…ìugol yaltirgal teleren ka kammuuli e ka leydi, haray yehee. Si wanaa tun, on hattantaa wa…óugol …óum, si wanaa e doole e …ìanngannduyee. Ko honno non he…ìirton feere …óum?"
  55,34,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,35,"Hino wurtee e mon, onon jinna e yim…ìe, …óemngal yiite nge jillaa curki, e curki ki jillaa yiite. On waawaa ha…óitaade e …óum."
  55,36,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,37,"Si wonii kammu ngun seekorii jippagol Malaa'ika'en iwa e maggu, ngu wojjira wa pentiir bo…óe."
  55,38,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."
  55,39,"Nde √±alaande mawnde, wanaa ne…ó…óo maa jinna, woni ko lamnditoytee fii junuubi mun, tawde Allah no humpitii fii golle ma…ì…ìe …óen."
  55,40,"Ko hon…ói e neemaaji Allah …óuu…óu…ói e mo'on, woni ko fennaton onon denndaangal jinneeji e yim…ìe ?."